WoWMacroSet.Name: CompleteWarlock
WoWMacroSet.Description:
This is a complete set of class specific macros for the warlock.
The keybinds used are all Shift+Alt+something
It includes individual spell macros for all spells and talent spells. The format of the macros is: /cast Spell, or (for those designated "damage over time, dot") /castsequence reset=target spell, null
